OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,FA woman accused of murder told police
OL,8,Fshe asked her husband for a divorce
OL,9,Fand he threatened to kill her before
OL,10,Fshe allegedly stabbed him in the back.
OL,12,FChristine Rawle, 70, at their home in
OL,13,Fnorth Devon. She denies murder.
OL,15,FJurors were shown video footage of Mrs
OL,16,FRawle's police interview the day after
OL,17,Fher husband's death.
OL,19,FShe told detectives she had come into
OL,20,Fsome money, through a negligence
OL,21,Fclaim, and this made Mr Rawle angry.
