OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"I could not live with him the way he
OL,8,Fwas treating me, I was scared of him",
OL,9,FMrs Rawle said.
OL,11,F"He said I would never get any money,
OL,12,Fand when I said 'I have, here it is',
OL,13,Fhe got worse, much worse.
OL,15,F"I said to him 'I can't put up with
OL,16,Fthe way you're treating me, I'm going
OL,17,Fto divorce you.'
