OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"You can't live as a second-class
OL,8,Fcitizen, with someone saying they are
OL,9,Fgoing to kill you, because you want to
OL,10,Fbe free. I was petrified. I was
OL,11,Fabsolutely petrified."
OL,13,FMrs Rawle said the couple were doing
OL,14,Fjobs at their smallholding near
OL,15,FBraunton, including cleaning out horse
OL,16,Fmanure, on the day in question.
OL,18,FIan Rawle died from a single stab
OL,19,Fwound, but Mrs Rawle told detectives
OL,20,Fshe could not remember stabbing him.
