OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"He was shouting so much," she said.
OL,9,F"If you're saying he got stabbed and I
OL,10,Fwas the only one there, it had to be
OL,11,Fme. But I don't remember stabbing him.
OL,12,FI don't remember. It seems like a
OL,13,Fdream."
OL,15,FMrs Rawle said her husband called her
OL,16,Fa "liar" and threatened to kill her.
OL,18,F"We had a long conversation in which
OL,19,Fhe made it quite clear that he had
OL,20,Fevery intention of killing me," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
