OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"I tried to talk him out of it, but he
OL,8,Fwould not let it go."
OL,10,FWhen Mrs Rawle was being booked in by
OL,11,Fpolice officers after her arrest, she
OL,12,Ftold them: "I just snapped, I could
OL,13,Fnot take any more."
OL,15,FIn her interview the following day,
OL,16,Fshe claimed her husband was
OL,17,F"systematically abusing" her.
OL,19,F"There are people who think I've done
OL,20,Fthis for financial gain, but I
OL,21,Fdidn't," she said.
