OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"I didn't need his money. I saw a
OL,8,Ffuture. I didn't need him."
OL,10,FAsked why she stayed with her husband
OL,11,Fif he was threatening her, she said:
OL,12,F"The way it worked with us rowing, the
OL,13,Fmoment I backed down it would all be
OL,14,Fpeace.
OL,16,F"I couldn't have him systematically
OL,17,Fbully me, and that led up to me
OL,18,Frealising that at my age I needed to
OL,19,Fleave. And this was the opportunity,
OL,20,Fwith the money.
