OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"He only got angry when I brought up
OL,8,Fagain about getting divorced.
OL,10,F"I said to him 'I cannot live with you
OL,11,Fbecause you're threatening me.'"
OL,13,FMrs Rawle added: "He was everything to
OL,14,Fme, and he treated me so badly, and
OL,15,Fwhen I found a way of getting away
OL,16,Ffrom him, he decided he was going to
OL,17,Fhurt me. Hurt me badly."
