OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,FShe also told police her husband had
OL,8,Fmade a 'slitting throat' gesture and
OL,9,Fimplied she was 'mental' just moments
OL,10,Fbefore his death.
OL,12,FSpeaking to detectives after her
OL,13,Farrest, Christine Rawle said she had
OL,14,Fbeen arguing with her husband, Ian, at
OL,15,Ftheir home in north Devon.
OL,17,FMrs Rawle was on the phone to her
OL,18,Fdaughter, Chiez, asking for her help.
