OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"He was going like this (slit throat)
OL,8,Fto me," she said during her police
OL,9,Finterview.
OL,11,F"That was going on for quite a while
OL,12,Fbefore I phoned Chiez."
OL,14,FMrs Rawle told police her husband made
OL,15,Fa gesture, twirling his finger around
OL,16,Fnext to his head, suggesting his wife
OL,17,Fwas insane.
OL,19,FShe added that Mr Rawle had been "my
OL,20,Fcaptor". "Years ago he was my dream
OL,21,Fpartner," she said.
