OL,3,C'I was petrified': Woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurder says husband threatened to kill
OL,5,Cher
OL,7,F"Over the years a lot of things have
OL,8,Fhappened and I have always been made
OL,9,Fto back down.
OL,11,F"Lots of things have happened that I
OL,12,Fwould be ashamed to say. Lots of
OL,13,Fthings have happened to my animals."
OL,15,FChristine Rawle denies murder and the
OL,16,Ftrial continues.
